Exit fullscreen mode

This lets TypeScript's type checker run faster and more accurately on complex generic types! 🏎️

🎉 Wrapping Up

TypeScript 7 is a landmark release that brings:

• ⚡ Dramatically faster builds with Isolated Declarations

• 🎯 Stricter type safety that catches more bugs

• 🧩 Better ergonomics with named tuples and improved satisfies

• 🚀 Modern async support with AsyncContext

• 💎 Production-ready decorators with metadata

• 🔬 Fine-grained variance control for generics

Whether you're building the next big SaaS, a mobile app with React Native, or maintaining a massive enterprise codebase — TypeScript 7 has something for everyone. 💪

Are you excited about TypeScript 7? Drop a comment below and let me know which feature you're most hyped about! 👇🔥

Happy coding! 🧑‍💻✨
